            "answer_text": "There are a lot of Content Writing Courses available online free of cost. You can enroll and get started with learning. You can find some of the best Content Writing Courses on ECT, Udemy, Coursera, EdX, etc. Apart from these courses you can also check out YouTube videos that offer insights on Content Writing and help its audience develop skills. There are videos on content Writing Tutorials for beginners, Content Writing Tools, and other content related topics. One such on-going series that I have been following since November 2019 is \u2018The Logophile\u2019s Lounge\u2019 available on ECT YouTube Channel. In this series, Mr. Saket Kumar Singh, founder and instructor at ECT, effectively discusses ways to master the art of Content Writing. The videos not only cover basic writing skills but also introduce the best writing practices that industry experts avail. The videos are uploaded on the channel on a weekly basis and discover ways to monetize your writing. There are 20 videos in this series as of now, the last one was added yesterday only. Watch them and learn content writing during this pandemic. Disclaimer: I have been a part of ECT\u2019s online Content Writing Course. Happy Learning! ",
